# AgentMaster dependency pins (optional supply-chain guard)
#
# By default the auto-updater pulls the latest default branch of every
# third-party skill repo every 6 hours — which means a compromised upstream
# repo would flow straight into your ~/.claude/skills/. Pinning a repo locks
# it to an exact, reviewed commit instead.
#
# Format: one line per repo, <name>=<full 40-char commit sha>
# Valid names: caveman, superpowers, claude-skills, claude-mem, impeccable
# Unpinned repos keep tracking the latest default branch.
#
# To pin: look up the commit on GitHub, review the diff, then add e.g.
# caveman=0123456789abcdef0123456789abcdef01234567
